                "caption": "Figure 1:Radar comparison ofQwen3-1.7Bperformance on AfriMGSM under a 4096-token generation budget.\nEach axis corresponds to one of the 17 low-resource African languages, with axis-specific scaling based on the maximum observed performance for that language.\nCOPSD consistently outperforms both the base and GRPO-trained models across languages.",
